    {
      "id": "1ece1d2e-a34b-46d0-b5f1-059e43245d2b",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Co-training is one form of semi-supervised classification that has historically exhibited good predictive results that has, to the author’s best knowledge not been implemented in education. Moreover, the literature lacks solutions in regression. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1ece1d2e-a34b-46d0-b5f1-059e43245d2b",
